# Day 2 Project
# Tip Calculator
bill = float(input("Welcome to tip calculator./nWhat was the total bill ? "))
procentage = int(input("What procentage would you like to give (int pls) ? "))
nr_people = int(input("How many people to split ? "))
print(f"Each person should pay {round(((bill+procentage/100*bill)/nr_people),2)}")
